 :                                                                            :
 : Mastering 3D Printing shows you how to get the most out of your printer,   :
 : including how to design models, choose materials, work with different      :
 : printers, and integrate 3D printing with traditional prototyping to make   :
 : techniques like sand casting more efficient.                               :
 :                                                                            :
 : You've printed key chains. You've printed simple toys. Now you're ready to :
 : innovate with your 3D printer to start a business or teach and inspire     :
 : others.                                                                    :
 :                                                                            :
 : Joan Horvath has been an educator, engineer, author, and startup 3D        :
 : printing company team member. She shows you all of the technical details   :
 : you need to know to go beyond simple model printing to make your 3D printer:
 : work for you as a prototyping device, a teaching tool, or a business       :
 : machine
